Preparing and conducting an excursion or compiling the project for an event at non-university institutions, participating in educational projects. Applying one's creative and analytical skills by working in an enterprise. Supervisors are needed on the behalf of the university and the trainee base for conducting practical training. After the end of the training the trainee base's supervisor gives feedback to the supervisor of university's side, how the trainee managed with his/her tasks, developed during the training, what kind of preparations were made by the student for the training, etc.Objectives/eesmärkid:  During the course students can practice in an institution outside of the university participating in different projects and academic tasks, and learn, how to start and conduct a project.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  After participating in practical training students recognize their abilities and appropriateness for different tasks, helping them in future career-choices.
